---
title: Smart Provencal-Style Fish Stew with Tarragon Aioli
description: This comforting stew, deeply flavoured with aromatics and sweetened with tomatoes, gets a zesty pick-me-up from tarragon and lemon. A dollop of garlicky aioli adds a hint of creaminess that makes this dinner unforgettable!
